title: Meatloaf: Three Bats Live
description:
WHOA GANG!!

Here&#039;s Meatloaf, back after quite a few years retirement from touring, and kickin&#039; it with all his hits! Featuring 2 of the HOTTEST backup singers I&#039;ve seen since a Poison concert, Meatloaf sings the hits from all 3 albums. This LIVE concert is 1 hour and 30 minutes long and is re-encoded for your viewing pleasure from an HD presentation on HD-NET.

Songs include "Bat out of Hell", "2 out of 3 Ain&#039;t Bad", "I Would do Anything for Love", and more plus a bonus cover of a Stones song for his encore&#039; (I won&#039;t spoil the surprise but, you will enjoy!)

Songs Include:

2 OUT OF 3 AIN&#039;T BAD
I WOULD DO ANYTHING FOR LOVE
PARADISE BY THE DASHBOARD LIGHTS
IT&#039;S ALL COMIN&#039; BACK TO ME NOW
BAT OUT OF HELL
(and a special Stones encore cover)
